  "panels": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "id": 891,
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### Multi-leg hedge → Prometheus（本页无 K 线）\n\n| 环节 | 频率 / 说明 |\n|------|-------------|\n| **Prometheus scrape** | **15s**（与 trend 共用 `prometheus.yml` global）|\n| **Daemon 主循环** | `MultiLegDaemon.poll_seconds`，默认 **30s**；每条 **已消费的 bar** 在 `run_once` 内更新 `mlbot_multi_leg_*`、事件与持仓 gauge |\n| **账户/健康** | `run_multi_leg_live` 里 `MLBOT_MARKET_DATA_INTERVAL`，默认 **30s**，刷新账户等 gauge |\n| **事件** | 每 bar **`bar_tick`**（heartbeat）；portfolio 否决 **`risk_reject`** + **`mlbot_multi_leg_risk_reject_codes_total{code}`**；同 symbol 多策略开仓冲突 **`symbol_conflict`**；approved **place / execution …** 在动作发生时写入；图上为 scrape 阶梯 |\n\n**「各层」**：以 **multi-leg 管道**（bars → actions → exec → risk_reject）为主；经典 `mlbot_funnel_total` 仅在该 job 也 flush 统计时才有数据。"
      },
      "transparent": false
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Hedge · daemon poll 总次数（Counter）",
      "id": 890,
      "gridPos": { "h": 3, "w": 8, "x": 0, "y": 6 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-monitoring" },
      "targets": [
        { "refId": "A", "expr": "mlbot_multi_leg_daemon_polls_total{job=~\"$job\"}", "instant": true }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "none" }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "values": false }, "colorMode": "value", "graphMode": "area" }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Hedge · bars 处理 rate（sum）",
      "id": 893,
      "gridPos": { "h": 3, "w": 8, "x": 8, "y": 6 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-monitoring" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum(rate(mlbot_multi_leg_bars_processed_total{job=~\"$job\",strategy=~\"${strategy:regex}\",symbol=~\"${symbol:regex}\"}[5m]))",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "ops" }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "values": false }, "colorMode": "value", "graphMode": "area" }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Hedge · CPU %",
      "id": 894,
      "gridPos": { "h": 3, "w": 8, "x": 16, "y": 6 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-monitoring" },
      "targets": [
        { "refId": "A", "expr": "mlbot_cpu_percent{job=~\"$job\"}", "instant": true }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "percent" }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "values": false }, "colorMode": "value", "graphMode": "area" }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Hedge · multi-leg 管道",
      "id": 312,
      "gridPos": { "h": 9, "w": 14, "x": 0, "y": 9 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-monitoring" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (strategy, symbol) (rate(mlbot_multi_leg_bars_processed_total{job=~\"$job\",strategy=~\"${strategy:regex}\",symbol=~\"${symbol:regex}\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "bars {{strategy}}/{{symbol}}"
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "expr": "sum by (strategy, symbol) (rate(mlbot_multi_leg_actions_total{job=~\"$job\",strategy=~\"${strategy:regex}\",symbol=~\"${symbol:regex}\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "actions {{strategy}}/{{symbol}}"
        },
        {
          "refId": "C",
          "expr": "sum by (strategy, symbol) (rate(mlbot_multi_leg_execution_results_total{job=~\"$job\",strategy=~\"${strategy:regex}\",symbol=~\"${symbol:regex}\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "exec {{strategy}}/{{symbol}}"
        },
        {
          "refId": "D",
          "expr": "sum by (strategy, symbol) (rate(mlbot_multi_leg_risk_rejected_total{job=~\"$job\",strategy=~\"${strategy:regex}\",symbol=~\"${symbol:regex}\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "risk_reject {{strategy}}/{{symbol}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": { "stacking": { "mode": "normal", "group": "B" } },
          "unit": "ops"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" } }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Hedge · 经典漏斗 / orders（若 job 产出）",
      "id": 313,
      "gridPos": { "h": 9, "w": 10, "x": 14, "y": 9 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-monitoring" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (strategy, stage) (rate(mlbot_funnel_total{job=~\"$job\",strategy=~\"${strategy:regex}\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{strategy}} · {{stage}}"
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "expr": "sum by (strategy) (rate(mlbot_orders_total{job=~\"$job\",strategy=~\"${strategy:regex}\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "orders {{strategy}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "unit": "ops", "custom": { "stacking": { "mode": "normal", "group": "C" } } },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" } }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Hedge · Risk veto by code（governor + symbol_conflict）",
      "id": 319,
      "gridPos": { "h": 7, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 18 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-monitoring" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (strategy, symbol, code) (rate(mlbot_multi_leg_risk_reject_codes_total{job=~\"$job\",strategy=~\"${strategy:regex}\",symbol=~\"${symbol:regex}\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{strategy}} {{symbol}} {{code}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "ops" }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" } }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Hedge · 事件（bar_tick / place / risk_reject / symbol_conflict / execution …）",
      "id": 315,
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 25 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-monitoring" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (strategy, event, side) (increase(mlbot_strategy_event_total{job=~\"$job\",scope=\"hedge\",strategy=~\"${strategy:regex}\",symbol=~\"${symbol:regex}\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{strategy}} {{event}} {{side}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": {}, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" } }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Hedge · 最近事件价",
      "id": 316,
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 33 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-monitoring" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "mlbot_strategy_event_price{job=~\"$job\",scope=\"hedge\",strategy=~\"${strategy:regex}\",symbol=~\"${symbol:regex}\"}",
          "legendFormat": "{{strategy}} {{event}} {{side}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "none" }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" } }
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "title": "Hedge · 持仓快照",
      "id": 317,
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 39 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-monitoring" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "max by (strategy, symbol, side) (mlbot_position_qty{job=~\"$job\",scope=\"hedge\",strategy=~\"${strategy:regex}\",symbol=~\"${symbol:regex}\"})",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "expr": "max by (strategy, symbol, side) (mlbot_position_notional_usdt{job=~\"$job\",scope=\"hedge\",strategy=~\"${strategy:regex}\",symbol=~\"${symbol:regex}\"})",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": {}, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "showHeader": true }
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "title": "Hedge · 事件计数（时间轴）",
      "id": 318,
      "gridPos": { "h": 7, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 47 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-monitoring" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (strategy, event, side) (increase(mlbot_strategy_event_total{job=~\"$job\",scope=\"hedge\",strategy=~\"${strategy:regex}\",symbol=~\"${symbol:regex}\"}[$__range]))",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": {}, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "showHeader": true }
    }
  ],
